# Smart NGO Resource Platform — Full Context Summary

## Project Overview

A full-stack monorepo web platform connecting **citizens in need** with **NGOs**. Citizens submit resource requests, NGOs review/fulfill them via a volunteer & resource management system, and a Super Admin oversees the entire platform.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 19 + Vite + TypeScript + TailwindCSS v4 (via `@tailwindcss/vite`) + shadcn/ui |
| Backend | Node.js + Express 5 + TypeScript |
| Database | MySQL / MariaDB |
| ORM | Prisma v7 with `@prisma/adapter-mariadb` (driver-adapter pattern — NOT the classic datasource URL pattern) |
| Auth | JWT (jsonwebtoken, 7-day expiry) + bcryptjs (12 rounds) |
| Validation | Zod v4 |
| State (FE) | Redux Toolkit + localStorage persistence |
| Testing | Jest + Supertest (integration tests) |
| Dev server (BE) | ts-node-dev |
| Dev server (FE) | Vite |

