### Requests — `/api/v1/requests`
| Method | Path | Auth | Role | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/v1/requests` | Bearer | Any authenticated | Create a help request |
| GET | `/api/v1/requests/mine` | Bearer | Any authenticated | Own requests only |
| GET | `/api/v1/requests/stats` | Bearer | NGO_ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN | Counts by status |
| GET | `/api/v1/requests` | Bearer | NGO_ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN | All PENDING + UNDER_REVIEW |
| GET | `/api/v1/requests/:id` | Bearer | Any authenticated | Citizens only see own; NGO/Admin see all |
| PATCH | `/api/v1/requests/:id/status` | Bearer | NGO_ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN | Update status |

**POST /requests body:**
```json
{
  "title": "...",         // min 5 chars
  "description": "...",   // min 20 chars
  "category": "FOOD",     // FOOD|MEDICAL|SHELTER|EDUCATION|CLOTHING|FINANCIAL|OTHER
  "urgencyLevel": 5,      // 1–5, default 1
  "address": "...",
  "city": "...",
  "state": "..."
}
```

**PATCH /:id/status body:**
```json
{ "status": "APPROVED", "rejectionReason": "..." }
```
`rejectionReason` required only when `status = REJECTED`.

**Stats response shape:**
```json
{ "PENDING":10, "UNDER_REVIEW":3, "APPROVED":5, "REJECTED":2, "IN_PROGRESS":1, "COMPLETED":8, "CANCELLED":0, "TOTAL":29 }
