## Middleware Stack

| Middleware | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `helmet` | Secure HTTP headers |
| `cors` | Allows `localhost:*` and `127.0.0.1:*` origins only, `credentials: true` |
| `morgan('dev')` | HTTP request logging |
| `express.json()` | Parse JSON bodies |
| `authenticate` | Verifies Bearer JWT, populates `req.user = { userId, role }` |
| `authorize(...roles)` | Variadic role check — used in requests/volunteers/resources routers |
| `requireRole(...roles)` | Same logic — used in ngo/admin routers |
| `validate(schema)` | Parses `req.body` through a Zod schema; throws on failure |
| `errorHandler` | Global: handles `AppError` (custom), `ZodError` (400), and unexpected errors (500) |

