| `/ngo/requests` | `NGODashboard` | `PrivateRoute` | NGO_ADMIN |
| `/ngo/resources` | `ResourcesPage` | `RoleRoute` | NGO_ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN |
| `/volunteer/dashboard` | `VolunteerDashboardPage` | `RoleRoute` | VOLUNTEER |
| `/admin` | `AdminPanel` | `PrivateRoute` | SUPER_ADMIN |
| `*` | Redirect to `/` | — | — |

### Route Guards
- **`PrivateRoute`**: If `!isAuthenticated` → `/login`. If `allowedRoles` set and role doesn't match → `/dashboard`.
- **`RoleRoute`**: If `!isAuthenticated` → `/login`. If role not in `allowedRoles` → `/dashboard`.
- **`PublicOnlyRoute`** (inline in index.tsx): If `isAuthenticated` → `/dashboard`.

